    <p class="gd-lede">Iceland is closer than most guests imagine, and the journey to the heliskiing base in the far north is refreshingly simple. This chapter walks you through flying in, choosing between <a href="/travel-here">Keflavík and Akureyri</a>, reaching <a href="/siglo-hotel">Siglufjörður</a>, the transfers we handle for you, and how to build a full Iceland adventure around your week of skiing.</p>
